          </div> 
        </li>
        
        <li class="our-values__box our-values-swiper__item swiper-slide">
          <input class="our-values__field" type="radio" id="tab_3" name="tab-group">
          <label for="tab_3" class="our-values__figure">
            <svg class="truth" height="155px" width="155px">
              <use xlink:href="#quality_icon"></use>
            </svg>
          </label> 
          <div class="our-values__content">
            <h3 class="our-values-content__title">The Quality</h3>
            <p class="our-values-content__description body-medium">Quality isn't something we take lightly. It’s not easy maintaining the power of nature in its purest form and bringing it to thousands of people across the world, but where there’s a (good) will there’s a way. We want effectiveness over great marketing so that people can truly live happier and healthier lives; and that means we’ll never cut corners.</p>
          </div> 
        </li>
        
        <li class="our-values__box our-values-swiper__item swiper-slide">
          <input class="our-values__field" type="radio" id="tab_4" name="tab-group">
          <label for="tab_4" class="our-values__figure">
            <svg class="truth" height="155px" width="155px">
              <defs>
                <polygon id="path-1" points="0 0.737 76.2629 0.737 76.2629 76.9998 0 76.9998"></polygon>
              </defs>
              <use xlink:href="#planet_icon"></use>
            </svg>
          </label> 
          <div class="our-values__content">
            <h3 class="our-values-content__title">The Earth</h3>
            <p class="our-values-content__description body-medium">We want to better humankind and also better the earth in the process. We want to rekindle the relationship that humans have to nature and empower both parties as a result. Humans actually have an endocannabinoid system that interacts with CBD, so really, we’re just nature’s matchmakers. We also only use organic farming practices that support the ecosystem and use eco-packaging, and for every order made, we plant a tree.</p>
          </div> 
